title: Sound On: Stalemate Over Biden Agenda Vote (Radio)
itunes:title: Sound On: Stalemate Over Biden Agenda Vote (Radio)
description:
Bloomberg Washington Correspondent Joe Mathieu delivers insight and analysis on the latest headlines from the White House and Capitol Hill, including conversations with influential lawmakers and key figures in politics and policy.


Guests: Roger Fisk, Principal at New Day Strategy, Jennifer Kerns, GOP Strategist and former spokeswoman for the California Republican Party, Chuck Rocha, Founder of Nuestro PAC and Bloomberg Politics Contributor Rick Davis.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
